Class HttpServiceFactory

All Implemented Interfaces:
ServiceFactory
public class HttpServiceFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServiceFactory

This implementation of ServiceFactory makes returns to the client DynamicProxies to encapsulate the client calls in http protocol. The client sees its "normal" remote interface.

setServerContext

public void setServerContext(java.lang.String context)
